Subject: How To Be A Real Developer In Two Easy Steps
Description: Have some imposter syndrome? Worried that you aren't a *real* developer? You're in luck! There's an easy, anybody-can-do-it two-step process you can follow to conquer your fears and become a Real Developer. What are those two steps? Well...that's where it gets complicated. Come with Anne as she recounts her path into the world of software development, overcomes her fears, questions the nature of reality, and shows off a super cool Ruby script.   Speakers include:Anne Cahalan - Track: Tech  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: Projector
